data.description: Adorable cottage in a great location right off of Veterans. This two bedroom , one bath home has an eat-in kitchen with new engineered wood vinyl floor, new kitchen sink and new dishwasher. The bar top is a beautiful live edge wood with stools. There are new insulated windows. Original wood floors. Porch and a covered patio added in 2022. New roof in 2021. Huge fenced in back yard with new wooden fence great for entertaining. Attached one car garage and 2 car driveway for off street parking. Many beautiful flowering trees. BROKER TOUR FEBRUARY 27TH 12:00-2:00
